export const JobSectionData = {
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'An oportunitie for you',

    description:
        'Crystal System is a community of young and passionate technology enthusiasts.'+
        'If you are willing to learn, if you are ambitious, if you like challenges, we offer you a career with an international vision, diverse experiences and continuous growth.',
    buttonLabel: 'Join Us',
    imgStart: '',
    img: './images/job-search.png',
    alt: 'Vault'
};

export const homeObjThree = {
    lightBg: true,
    lightText: false,

    headline: 'Super fast and simple onboarding process',
    description:
      "Get everything set up and ready in under 10 minutes. All you need to do is add your information and you're ready to go.",

  };
